WEBVTT

00:02:30.357 --> 00:02:33.471
They posed an existential threat

00:02:33.495 --> 00:02:34.664
to no one.

00:02:35.561 --> 00:02:40.137
But we rearranged our entire
national security apparatus

00:02:40.161 --> 00:02:44.242
in the most sweeping way
since the end of the Second World War.

00:02:44.577 --> 00:02:46.416
We launched two wars.

00:02:46.440 --> 00:02:48.773
We spent trillions of dollars.

00:02:48.797 --> 00:02:50.974
We suspended our values.

00:02:50.998 --> 00:02:52.849
We violated international law.

00:02:52.873 --> 00:02:54.105
We embraced torture.

00:02:54.129 --> 00:02:55.802
We embraced the idea

00:02:55.826 --> 00:02:58.897
that if these 19 guys could do this,
anybody could do it.

